{"tid":711711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"電競不再是年輕人專利，多名60歲老人組成電競隊伍《Special Mission》首戰就奪冠！","createTime":"2018-06-21T18:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T08:14:42.000Z","uid":1886,"like":124,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"3ee608e222ce77a7ebec003ed32ecc5691d04b84","tid":711711,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T18:14:04.000Z","msg":"ACER 12日與長者安居協會合辦「老友鬼鬼電競交流賽」，18位經過電競訓練的銀齡長者們與ACER員工組隊進行「暴雪英霸」對戰，別少看這些長者的身手與技術，他們經過10課專業訓練後，無論控制能力與戰術均有板有眼，最終由全女班戰隊「Special Mission」奪得冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n電競打機，一直看似都只是年輕人的專利，但對於一班銀齡長者來說，他們的眼中並沒有合適不合適，更坦言「年齡並唔係一個問題」，這份積極的人生態度，對於現在的你來說，是否經已缺少呢？<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Elder_WorldCupTuning_01-768x432.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2FElder_WorldCupTuning_01-768x432.png&h=3b374a44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/unwirehk/videos/10160792732595495/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Funwirehk%2Fvideos%2F10160792732595495%2F&d=hV3d%2BsYnbk7YehZq6%2Ba1nMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=28ebd1bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/unwirehk/videos/10160792732595495/</a></div><br />\n<br />\n近日長者安居協會跟贊助商 Acer，合作舉辦了「老友鬼鬼電競交流賽2018」，為的就是讓一班已上年紀的老友記，能夠接觸一些時下年輕人最熱門的玩意。電競交流賽中，老友記分別組成了 4 隊不同隊伍，而每隊均由 3 位銀齡長者及 2 位 Acer 員工組成，比賽過程及反應都相當熱烈，連筆者想也想不到，隊伍年齡高達 200 歲的長者，亦能有此表現，看來老友記的毅力確是不能輕看。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/002%E9%95%B702-1-768x432.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F002%25E9%2595%25B702-1-768x432.png&h=6febd739&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n銀齡長者 Carrie 學會玩《暴雪英霸》後稱，「我有一句名言加俾自己，我地玩電競就包無老人痴呆症」。看來打機對於一班老友記來說，也是一項相當健康的活動。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/001%E9%95%B704-768x430.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F001%25E9%2595%25B704-768x430.png&h=1cbfed1f&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n「揼佢啦！揼佢啦！」筆者一進入場地，雖然沒有電競比賽誇張的燈光效果，但長者樂也融融的氣氛絕不會比專業的電競比賽遜色。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/006%E9%95%B7-768x428.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F006%25E9%2595%25B7-768x428.png&h=a38c199b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/06/21/schsa-acer/headline/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2Fschsa-acer%2Fheadline%2F&d=hV3d%2BsYnbk7YehZq6%2Ba1nMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=e735c039\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/06/21/schsa-acer/headline/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/16883/咩話_長者電競大賽_玩暴雪英霸___唔信...._去片\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F16883%2F%E5%92%A9%E8%A9%B1_%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%B6%E5%A4%A7%E8%B3%BD_%E7%8E%A9%E6%9A%B4%E9%9B%AA%E8%8B%B1%E9%9C%B8___%E5%94%94%E4%BF%A1...._%E5%8E%BB%E7%89%87&d=hV3d%2BsYnbk7YehZq6%2Ba1nMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=c51b31d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/16883/咩話_長者電競大賽_玩暴雪英霸___唔信...._去片</a></div>"},{"pid":"705bababb4d6ce5416a9d8f0191df0623562cbd5","tid":711711,"uid":1886,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T18:21:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>親身落場打機  更明年輕人心態</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n相信各位巴絲打機時，總會試過被屋企人催促吃飯，或被女友報以不滿的情況，而這次冠軍隊伍的銀齡長者 Carrie 亦笑著說「我記得我個仔讀書嘅時候呢，成日沉迷打機，咁佢打機我就打佢㗎啦」，看來要明白打機人仕的心情，對於上一輩來說，絕對不是容易的事。幸好，透過這次活動，Carrie 可稱得上真正明白年輕人的心態，「自從我學左打機之後，我知道打機真係唔可以半途停低架」，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>其後她更稱「打機，唔止係電子遊戲，係一個體育項目呀嘛，係值得推廣架。」</strong></span>看來年輕人要上一輩明白某些事情，就是要讓他們親自嘗試一下，可惜，現實上總有些事，是永遠也嘗試不了的。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/021547_6b878604dcf1af70953dd0cda852037a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F021547_6b878604dcf1af70953dd0cda852037a.jpg&h=72156c8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲ 電競不只是年輕人運動。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/007%E9%95%B7-768x428.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F007%25E9%2595%25B7-768x428.png&h=06078995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲ 在談論戰術時，長者認真的表情及投入程度，確實會嚇你一跳。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/005%E9%95%B7-768x430.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F005%25E9%2595%25B7-768x430.png&h=52ffa03e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲ 電競運動有益身心，除了反應要快，手力及腦力亦不能輕視。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/012%E9%95%B7-768x430.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F012%25E9%2595%25B7-768x430.png&h=7bb2fa01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲ 奪冠隊伍長者 Carrie 已達 68 歲。</span></div>"},{"pid":"41d06c21731e6fa3774b0aedac7225c41b590250","tid":711711,"uid":64380,"like":111,"dislike":2,"score":109,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T18:22:24.000Z","msg":"我老豆打pubg 打cod 打csgo叻過我好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f069d676f3dc2945d7c6515f1bf0c3bbac279c5","tid":711711,"uid":1886,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T18:23:21.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/014%E9%95%B7-768x427.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F014%25E9%2595%25B7-768x427.png&h=0dd78bfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲ Special Mission 隊伍得到冠軍後，表現極為興奮。</span></div>"},{"pid":"17757078f2272259927237af4d71a4b9061b3b23","tid":711711,"uid":60545,"like":96,"dislike":0,"score":96,"quote":{"pid":"6f069d676f3dc2945d7c6515f1bf0c3bbac279c5","tid":711711,"uid":1886,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T18:23:21.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/014%E9%95%B7-768x427.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F014%25E9%2595%25B7-768x427.png&h=0dd78bfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲ Special Mission 隊伍得到冠軍後，表現極為興奮。</span></div>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T18:24:41.000Z","msg":"咁興奮會唔會玩到爆血管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16bb338384fa2f05d6e69c822b0b1411d276286","tid":711711,"uid":26506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"41d06c21731e6fa3774b0aedac7225c41b590250","tid":711711,"uid":64380,"like":111,"dislike":2,"score":109,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T18:22:24.000Z","msg":"我老豆打pubg 打cod 打csgo叻過我好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T18:24:51.000Z","msg":"由細到大Civ都未贏過老豆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d6e36ed9014e56f98a371045a54569dd788a43b","tid":711711,"uid":64380,"like":38,"dislike":9,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"c16bb338384fa2f05d6e69c822b0b1411d276286","tid":711711,"uid":26506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"41d06c21731e6fa3774b0aedac7225c41b590250","tid":711711,"uid":64380,"like":111,"dislike":2,"score":109,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T18:22:24.000Z","msg":"我老豆打pubg 打cod 打csgo叻過我好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T18:24:51.000Z","msg":"由細到大Civ都未贏過老豆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T18:26:10.000Z","msg":"然後發現老母原來玩傳說對決係A排位，on9"},{"pid":"4f1b849d15add30a9e52760deaf0833cc6315477","tid":711711,"uid":1886,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T18:28:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>打破隔閡　盼跨代共融</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/25/144322_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F25%2F144322_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4a7e54a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">年輕人與老人要打破隔閡，有時候需要的，就是一個機會，一個能夠互相了解的機會。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n電競打機跟長者，本應是毫無交集，但為何兩者又會走在一起呢？原來主辦單位長者安居協會的老友網高級經理袁慧明表示，為的就是建立長者跟年輕一代的溝通橋樑，「我覺得電競就係時下年輕人好鐘意玩嘅野，希望等佢地亦都知道，依架後生仔係做緊啲乜野呢，等佢地有多啲溝通嘅機會」。但筆者卻在想，要為兩代人建立溝通橋樑，在行動上又是否真的像說那麼容易呢？誰不知銀齡長者 Carrie 的一句徹底把筆者想法改變了，她說：「我呢就同個仔講，如果我今次打到亞軍呢，我就返黎同你對打，咁依架真係願望成真啦」。兩代人甚至三代人，要打破隔閡，有時候需要的，就是一個機會，一個能夠互相了解的機會。"},{"pid":"c7a421068c092593a913205f5c12ee56b4b20024","tid":711711,"uid":140218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T18:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f13d5c5f1ed80f06cb7be517d8274c98bc5ad8f","tid":711711,"uid":104443,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T18:35:56.000Z","msg":"《暴雪英霸》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ffc7e3e8d628169e661c1592ef4a7b52cdda13a","tid":711711,"uid":97240,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T21:21:53.000Z","msg":"呢樣野真係要大大力推動<br />\n起碼俾班老一輩用下個腦"},{"pid":"b243385afefbc038aee24a0d1347c920f8bf5776","tid":711711,"uid":70487,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T21:50:05.000Z","msg":"仲以為玩俄羅絲方塊"},{"pid":"264c9e6691bbc68ed8d64afc095ab57ec380c6ff","tid":711711,"uid":82929,"like":3,"dislike":18,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T22:23:59.000Z","msg":"暴雪英霸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 班老野玩得掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n世界變"},{"pid":"9330d89c81951147952f4d871a067dd038d793cb","tid":711711,"uid":179967,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T22:34:38.000Z","msg":"我一早就已經想買部電腦俾我老豆打機睇咸片"},{"pid":"d95a78f625608ee72af45bf347e4ba8cb3451743","tid":711711,"uid":133450,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T22:36:40.000Z","msg":"妹下妹下都打贏你"},{"pid":"10486e760c8cd3c014c9d2f89954d3ca562a40c1","tid":711711,"uid":44171,"like":2,"dislike":33,"score":-31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T23:01:17.000Z","msg":"邊有可能, 老人家反應慢好多, 擺明係做新聞啦, d相都係擺pose影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f684f8493c8f2bde26cdb8452116a0fcb2e496f1","tid":711711,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17757078f2272259927237af4d71a4b9061b3b23","tid":711711,"uid":60545,"like":96,"dislike":0,"score":96,"quote":{"pid":"6f069d676f3dc2945d7c6515f1bf0c3bbac279c5","tid":711711,"uid":1886,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T18:23:21.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/014%E9%95%B7-768x427.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F014%25E9%2595%25B7-768x427.png&h=0dd78bfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲ Special Mission 隊伍得到冠軍後，表現極為興奮。</